body:
The command prints the following output if it succeeds. If the command
fails, see [Troubleshoot Errors](adf-create-store-cmd-errors) for recommended solutions.**S3:**S3 Configuration```json&#xA;&#x20;:copyable:&#x20;false
{
  "ok": 1,
  "store": {
    "name": "<store-name>",
    "region": "<region-name>",
    "bucket": "<bucket-name>",
    "additionalStorageClasses": ["<storage-classes>"]
    "delimiter": "<delimiter>",
    "provider": "<storage-provider>"
  }
}
```**Azure:**Azure Configuration```json&#xA;&#x20;:copyable:&#x20;false
{
  "ok": 1,
  "store": {
    "name": "<store-name>",
    "region": "<region-name>",
    "serviceURL": "<service-account-URL>",
    "containerName": "<storage-container-name>"
    "delimiter": "<delimiter>",
    "provider": "<storage-provider>"
  }
}
```**Gcp:**GCP Configuration```json&#xA;&#x20;:copyable:&#x20;false
{
  "ok": 1,
  "store": {
    "name": "<store-name>",
    "region": "<region-name>",
    "bucket": "<storage-container-name>"
    "delimiter": "<delimiter>",
    "prefix": "<prefix>",
    "provider": "<storage-provider>"
  }
}
```**Atlas:**Atlas Configuration```json
{
        "ok" : 1,
        "store" : {
                "name" : "<store-name>",
                "provider" : "<storage-provider>",
                "clusterName" : "<cluster-name>",
                "projectId" : "<project-id>",
                "readPreference" : {
                       "mode" : "<read-preference-mode>",
                       "tagSets" : [[{"name": "<name>", "value": "<value>"},...],...],
                       "maxStalenessSeconds" : <number-of-seconds>
                }
        }
}
```**Http:**HTTP Configuration```json
{
        "ok" : 1,
        "store" : {
                "name" : "<store-name>",
                "provider" : "<storage-provider>",
                "allowInsecure" : true|false,
                "urls" : [
                        "<url>"
                ],
                "defaultFormat: "<file-extension>"
        }
}
```**Oa:**Atlas Online Archive Configuration```json
{
  ok: 1,
  store: {
    name: '<store-name>',
    provider: 'dls:aws',
    region: '<online-archive-region>'
  }
}
```
